---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const updated = '13 March 2026';
---

<BaseLayout title="Terms of Service" description="Terms of Service for Turn1Visuals and the T1V App.">

  <section class="tos-section">
    <div class="container tos-inner">

      <header class="tos-header">
        <p class="section-label">Legal</p>
        <h1 class="tos-title">Terms of Service</h1>
        <p class="tos-meta">Last updated: {updated}</p>
      </header>

      <div class="prose">

        <p>
          These Terms of Service apply to the Turn1Visuals website at <a href="https://turn1visuals.com">turn1visuals.com</a>
          and the T1V App desktop application developed by Turn1Visuals. By using either, you agree to these terms.
        </p>

        <h2>1. About Turn1Visuals</h2>
        <p>
          Turn1Visuals is a personal Formula 1 content project. This website and its associated tools are operated
          by the owner of Turn1Visuals and are not affiliated with Formula 1, FOM, or FIA.
          Contact: <a href="mailto:info@turn1visuals.com">info@turn1visuals.com</a>
        </p>

        <h2>2. Website Use</h2>
        <p>
          The Turn1Visuals website provides F1 content, race data, and live stream information for personal and
          informational use. You may not copy, redistribute, or use the content for commercial purposes without
          prior written permission.
        </p>
        <p>
          All F1-related data, team names, driver names, and related trademarks are the property of their
          respective owners. Turn1Visuals makes no claim of ownership over any Formula 1 intellectual property.
        </p>

        <h2 id="t1v-app">3. T1V App</h2>
        <p>
          The T1V App ("the App") is a personal-use Electron desktop application developed by Turn1Visuals
          for managing live streaming sessions and uploading Formula 1 video content to social media platforms
          including TikTok, YouTube, and Twitch.
        </p>

        <h3>Use of the App</h3>
        <p>
          The App is intended for use by the owner of the Turn1Visuals account. It is provided free of charge
          and without warranty. You may not copy, distribute, or modify the App without prior written permission.
        </p>

        <h3>Third-party API integrations</h3>
        <p>
          The T1V App integrates with third-party platforms via their official APIs. Use of these integrations
          is subject to each platform's own Terms of Service:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li><a href="https://www.tiktok.com/legal/page/global/terms-of-service/en" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">TikTok Terms of Service</a></li>
          <li><a href="https://www.youtube.com/t/terms" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">YouTube Terms of Service</a></li>
          <li><a href="https://www.twitch.tv/p/legal/terms-of-service/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Twitch Terms of Service</a></li>
        </ul>

        <h3>Content responsibility</h3>
        <p>
          The user is solely responsible for all content uploaded or streamed via the App. All content must
          comply with the terms and community guidelines of the target platforms.
        </p>

        <h3>Data and privacy</h3>
        <p>
          The App does not transmit any personal data to servers operated by Turn1Visuals. All configuration
          data and OAuth tokens are stored locally on your device. See our
          <a href="/privacy">Privacy Policy</a> for full details.
        </p>

        <h2>4. Disclaimer</h2>
        <p>
          This website and the T1V App are provided "as is" without warranties of any kind. Turn1Visuals
          makes no guarantees regarding accuracy, availability, or fitness for any particular purpose.
          Use is at your own risk.
        </p>

        <h2>5. Limitation of Liability</h2>
        <p>
          To the maximum extent permitted by law, Turn1Visuals shall not be liable for any indirect,
          incidental, or consequential damages arising from use of this website or the T1V App.
        </p>

        <h2>6. Changes to These Terms</h2>
        <p>
          These Terms may be updated from time to time. The date at the top of this page reflects the
          most recent revision. Continued use after changes are posted constitutes acceptance of the
          updated Terms.
        </p>

        <h2>Contact</h2>
        <p>
          For questions about these Terms, contact Turn1Visuals at
          <a href="mailto:info@turn1visuals.com">info@turn1visuals.com</a>.
        </p>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .tos-section {
    padding-block: var(--space-section);
  }

  .tos-inner {
    max-width: 720px;
  }

  .tos-header {
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .tos-title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    line-height: 1;
    margin-block: 0.75rem 0.5rem;
  }

  .tos-meta {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--color-muted);
  }

  .prose {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1rem;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--color-muted);
  }

  .prose h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 1rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
    padding-top: 1.5rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .prose h2:first-of-type {
    margin-top: 0;
    padding-top: 0;
    border-top: none;
  }

  .prose h3 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
  }

  .prose ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.4rem;
  }

  .prose ul li {
    padding-left: 1.2rem;
    position: relative;
  }

  .prose ul li::before {
    content: '—';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--color-accent);
  }

  .prose a {
    color: var(--color-accent);
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 2px;
  }

  .prose code {
    font-size: 0.85em;
    color: var(--color-text);
    background: var(--color-border);
    padding: 0.1em 0.4em;
  }

  .prose strong {
    color: var(--color-text);
    font-weight: 600;
  }
</style>
